Package frc.team_8840_lib.controllers

Class SwerveModuleOld

java.lang.Object
frc.team_8840_lib.utils.IO.IOLayer
frc.team_8840_lib.controllers.SwerveModuleOld
public class SwerveModuleOld extends IOLayer
This class is used to control a swerve module. It is meant to be used with the SwerveDrive class. Sources: https://www.chiefdelphi.com/t/adapting-364s-base-swerve-drive-code-to-use-neos-for-steering/418402/3 Team 364 Team 3512
